  "2134980": {
    "name": "Soul Dier - Part 1",
    "steam_appid": 2134980,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134980/extras/1f7461c58ee7d9cf81340acbb38689d3.poster.avif?t=1761314306\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134980/extras/1f7461c58ee7d9cf81340acbb38689d3.webm?t=1761314306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134980/extras/1f7461c58ee7d9cf81340acbb38689d3.mp4?t=1761314306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >展开一场重拾记忆的旅程，探究神秘世界的秘密。与队友并肩作战，对抗强大的邪恶军团！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏分为上下两集（Part 1及Part 2），而Part 2目前仍在开发中。此产品「凋灵战士 Soul Dier - Part 1」只包括Part 1、并不包括Part 2。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经典日系战棋的回合制棋盘战斗系统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134980/extras/047862cc0e241650ef01668eedfe2a13.avif?t=1761314306\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏以远距离射击为主轴，因此位置部署和掩体／障碍物的利用尤其重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134980/extras/8bfec5b8d0c485f19d6d975743a85802.avif?t=1761314306\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134980/extras_big/8bfec5b8d0c485f19d6d975743a85802.avif?t=1761314306 width=800 height=262 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >明快的游戏节奏：分散玩家和敌人回合的排队系统、远距离为主的技能、较短的敌人回合、以及加速动画的选项。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134980/extras/2f75cb9f1853f839b852c5758c6db0dd.avif?t=1761314306\" width=1560 height=580 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过30关精心设计的关卡，提供约20小时的游玩时间（part 1）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有充数的重複关卡，每一关都有着全新的地图，同时亦会出现新的敌人兵种或特别机关！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134980/extras/83cb9bf5de7540216c30561cec3d17b5.avif?t=1761314306\" width=1560 height=870 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >具有挑战性的同时，游戏亦会公平地提供所有必要的战斗资讯，你必须不断应付刻意设计的敌人技能和关卡机制才能获胜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134980/extras/3dab7f55a710c4ae0b10f31b6624ad94.avif?t=1761314306\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134980/extras_big/3dab7f55a710c4ae0b10f31b6624ad94.avif?t=1761314306 width=800 height=376 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个角色都有着截然不同的设计，他们各自的强处和弱处将会互补不足。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134980/extras/748f33e0c602e3cf190da65de6b83758.avif?t=1761314306\" width=1560 height=636 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简洁的升级系统，完全毋须刷等。比起传统透过累积经验值来逐渐获得少许数值提升，这款游戏会在每关结束后自动解锁具有实际影响力的奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134980/extras/32e3fd7ae6ece4a455e8547f36332956.avif?t=1761314306\" width=1560 height=510 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有任何角色重置成本，儘管随时在战斗前利用徽章、道具和角色升级自订你的战斗配置，为下一场战斗做作最妥当的准备。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有道具只会在关卡内消耗而不会真的永久地减少，所以不要再囤积道具喇！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134980/extras/02d7268caa3ba37cc647cb42429ca3c1.avif?t=1761314306\" width=1560 height=706 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >个性鲜明的角色、幽默诙谐的对白，在每个关卡的过场动画探索充满神秘色彩的世界。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结识新伙伴、遭遇强大的邪恶军团、向挚友道别。一场从现代都市废墟到中世纪孤岛小镇的大冒险正等待着你！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134980/extras/8eb6933b71aaa55c69f5ea76ea709d4a.avif?t=1761314306\" width=1560 height=586 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过40首原创音乐（part 1），全由两位开发者亲自创作。从悠闲的爵士乐到激昂的金属战斗音乐应有尽有。</p></li></ul>",
